pageContext.claim: “IIhan Omar, a member of AOC Plus 3, will win us the Great State of Minnesota. The new face of the Democrat Party! ”
pageContext.analysis: Trump shared a tweet (later deleted) from comedian and conservative commentator Terrence K. Williams, who claimed that Democratic Rep. Ilhan Omar was dancing on the anniversary of the September 11, 2001, terrorist attacks. But the the footage of Omar dancing was from September 13.
